00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:35,360
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}Yes, ever since

335
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:38,560
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}I left your house.

336
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,560
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}I mean, it was there when I went to bed.

337
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:44,360
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}I'm thinking maybe they don't last.

338
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:48,120
