00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,120
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}No! Sparky!

340
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,360
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}- Sparky!

341
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:11,560
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}Don't worry. I can fix that, too.

342
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,640
