350
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,000
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}We could use a test dummy or something.

351
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:01,240
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}...seven, six, five...

