00:45:45,280 --> 00:45:47,760
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}Praise be New Holland

402
00:45:47,840 --> 00:45:49,080
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}No! Shh. No!

