00:45:51,560 --> 00:45:53,160
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}No, no, no! Shh!

404
00:45:54,760 --> 00:45:56,090
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}Victor?

