00:49:50,840 --> 00:49:52,360
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}He brought back Sparky?

467
00:49:55,960 --> 00:49:57,120
{\fnCambria\fs22\1c&H45DFEC&\i1}Mmm.

